{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/Library_Header_and_Header_Capsule.png?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leap into an 2.5D action platformer that takes inspiration from the iconic gameplay of the old-school <i>Prince of Persia</i> games, but upgrades it with a unique swashbuckling combat system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Keep your wits as sharp as your blade, for only the most heroic, dashing, and (most importantly) <i>stylish</i> of swords-masters will make it out alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/style_withHeader_thinner.png?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/style_4.gif?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn style by fighting with flair - swing from chandeliers, trick enemies into attacking each other, kick bottles into your enemies, and any other clever maneuvers you can find. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Then use your Style to dazzle your enemies with powerful special abilities, turning the tables on even the most powerful foes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/labyrinthOfSecrets_withHeader.png?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/explore_03.gif?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each level is designed to encourage exploration, with mysterious secrets hidden throughout. Paths are interwoven, and every twist and turn can reveal either a marvelous new surprise... or a deadly trap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/changingDangers_withHeader.png?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/dangers_04.gif?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every room of the Palace is a handcrafted work of art, but the dangers within will change each time you fail. You must stay on your toes if you are to survive its perils!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/taleWithinTale_withHeader.png?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/suckedIntoBook_03.gif?t=1739188429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are Rodrigo Al-Ahzab, a lowly beggar whose only aim is to survive in the streets of Granada. When you are pulled into a magical book, you learn that there are things that matter to you even more than your own survival\u2026\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Created by one of the writers behind <i>SpecOps: The Line</i>, this is a story with depths hidden behind the simple facade... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739188429","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/page.bg.jpg?t=1739188429","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/02d91ca137651a2be66141268c381f27a3d5a66d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739188429","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite